Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Che ostinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:56.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ancora non vuoi fare\N quello che ti dico?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:06.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I tuoi ordini... \Nnon gli obbedirò mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:09.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Suppongo ti servano altre punizioni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Allora ti punirò quanto vuoi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:13.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,con questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Su, mettilo in bocca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ora fammi godere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:27.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Non metterò mai in bocca quella cosa schifosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mettilo in bocca, ho detto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.93,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ascolta cosa ti dico! Fai tutto quello che ti dico di fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Se mi disobbedisci, ti\N costringerò ad obbedire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Bene... bene...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Più forte, succhia più forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:49.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Così mi piace!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sto venendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ingoia tutto il mio sperma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.25,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come hai osato mordermi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cos'è quello sguardo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:14.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Akari, tu sei la mia schiava sessuale!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ora non puoi più fuggire da me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sii leale con me! La mia leale schiava sessuale!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:21.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:24.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Preferirei morire che\N diventare tua schiava!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:27.29,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Allora ti esporrò come una bambola
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,,una fredda, morta bambola!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ora sei solo mia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sarai per sempre al mio fianco.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.84,Internal,,0,0,0,,Qualcuno, mi aiuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:57.83,Internal,,0,0,0,,Liberatemi da quest'uomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.32,Internal,,0,0,0,,Qualcuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.66,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Chi... Chi farebbe una\N cosa così orribile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.52,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.58,Internal,,0,0,0,,Shinohara-san sulla pelle\N aveva le stesse bruciature...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che c'è, Ryuichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.35,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Emi-san, devi essere\N stata tu ad ucciderli.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.64,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi-kun? Che stai dicendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:12.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quella benda che hai sulla mano
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.22,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\i1}copre una bruciatura, vero?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:20.07,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tomoko-san, Oishi-san, e anche Shinohara-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,tutti avevano delle\N bruciature sul corpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.77,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Le bruciature sembrano\N di una pistola stordente
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.72,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,e, Emi-san,anche la bruciatura\N sulla tua mano è...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:30.97,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Esattamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.96,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Sono davvero \Nimpressionata, Ryuichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Emi-san, perché l'hai fatto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:42.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io ho solo eliminato le persone\Nche hanno ostacolato il mio padrone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.66,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu! Hai ucciso Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.66,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.64,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:03.22,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Lui è il mio padrone,\N Yoshimasa Okouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:08.75,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Okouchi? Non vorrai dire\N il padrone di quest'isola?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I seccatori devono sparire ora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.26,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ora andate, voi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.08,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,M-Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.34,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Andate subito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:20.97,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Va bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.53,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Per ora andiamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:24.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:28.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takashi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non pensate a noi, andate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:31.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba-chan, ora\N dobbiamo andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,È meglio se smettete di resistere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:42.88,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba-chan! Scappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.00,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Svelta! Wakaba-chan, per favore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:44.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Visto che abbiamo nuove schiave come previsto
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:48.24,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,ti perdonerò di avergli fatto\N scoprire questo posto, Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,La ringrazio, Yoshimasa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:03.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Shoko-chan, non agitarti\N tanto per favore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Scusami, Hiromi-chan, non posso evitarlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Shoko... aiutami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hiromi-chan! Hiromi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Chi vi ha detto che\N potevate venire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Voi dovete eseguire alla lettera\N gli ordini di Yoshimasa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.87,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ora, chi renderà felice questo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:55.63,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:56.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non lo faremo mai quello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.87,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Agli ordini di Yoshimasa-sama\N non potete disobbedire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.55,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Volete altre punizioni?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.16,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Finalmente avete compreso\N la vostra posizione.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:12.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eccovi una ricompensa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.55,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Chi vi ha detto di fermarvi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:25.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ho organizzato questo viaggio\N misterioso per trovare nuove schiave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:29.74,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,E voi due siete state scelte.\NDovreste essere contente.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:34.97,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quella che è scappata\N dovrà unirsi a voi più tardi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:46.29,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Su, lo sperma di Yoshimasa-sama, \Nleccatelo tutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.04,Internal,,0,0,0,,Non venire, Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:07.47,Internal,,0,0,0,,Scappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.06,Internal,,0,0,0,,Wakaba! Scappa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.73,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Emi, che stai facendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.25,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Vieni ad aiutarmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.87,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì, Yoshimasa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.39,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non penso tu abbia tempo di preoccuparti della tua amica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:06.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu sarai la prossima, aspetta lì.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu hai quel che serve per essere mia schiava.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:19.49,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi prenderò cura di\N te se mi obbedisci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:23.07,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Guarda Akari. Dovresti essere gelosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Avresti potuto essere tu a servirmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:28.77,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ora basta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:33.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba! Takashi! Andiamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sama! Sta bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Inutile rifiuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Dannazione.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Li ucciderò tutti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sama? Sta bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa... sama! Perché?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ucciderò chiunque sia inutile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ucciderò chiunque mi disobbedisce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.51,Internal,,0,0,0,,Ucciderò chiunque mi disobbedisce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Cosa facciamo ora, Ryuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Comunque lasciamo\N l'isola al più presto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:36.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ma Ryuichi-san, non possiamo\N neanche chiedere aiuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.20,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Cosa faremo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.96,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Dobbiamo trovare\N un modo. Pensiamoci...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.88,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Che c'è, Wakaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:44.33,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Devo portare Ron con me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Dimentica quell'aloe per ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non voglio andarmene\N senza Ron-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba! Smettila di essere egoista!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Altrimenti mi arrabbierò davvero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No! deve venire con me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:04.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takashi, Hiromi-chan e\N Shoko-chan, occupatene tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Va bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:23.26,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace Ron-chan, posso portare solo questo pezzo con me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Andiamo, Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,L'isola che non ha alberi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:43.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io desidero poter vedere \Nquest'isola piena di alberi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.31,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quest'isola piena di alberi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.44,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takashi e gli altri, dove saranno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.03,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Avremmo dovuto scegliere\N un posto per incontrarci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:02.83,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Piuttosto... non abbiamo\N trovato l'ultimo capitolo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,per realizzare il nostro desiderio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non è il momento\N di parlare di questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Vi ho trovato finalmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,La vostra disobbedienza,\N la pagherete con la vita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.37,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Aspetta, lascia andare\N Wakaba per favore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.16,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Silenzio! È inutile pregare\N per le vostre vite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.30,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Vi ucciderò tutti!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:36.64,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.27,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, stai bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sciocca. Perché l'hai fatto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:56.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Se Onii-chan è salvo, va bene...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ora non parlare, Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:05.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io, ricordo che mi hai stretto\N tra le braccia così, prima...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.32,Internal,,0,0,0,,È vero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:14.92,Internal,,0,0,0,,Ho già tenuto tra le braccia\N Wakaba così, molto tempo fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Io, Onii-chan, ti proteggerò...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Non parlare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:23.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sempre... ti proteggerò sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:29.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba, riprenditi! Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Vi manderò tutti e\N due all'altro mondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:40.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Cos'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tu devi... essere quella di otto anni fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Allora, io ti ho ucciso.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.27,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perché sei qui? Perché sei qui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.39,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sama, giuro che\N sarò leale a lei tutta la vita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:14.57,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Perciò Yoshimasa-sama, \Ncon Emi... venga con Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yoshimasa-sa... sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:48.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,È passato tanto da quando ho visitato l'isola Oka, Yutaka onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Già, è vero...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.03,Flashback,,0,0,0,,La vista da qui non è cambiata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:02.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Già...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ron, te ne ricordi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sono passati due anni da quando hanno abbandonato l'isola.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.51,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Tuttavia, anche se il verde\N avrebbe dovuto ricoprire l'isola
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:16.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,in effetti le piante non possono crescere per l'acqua salata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Su, andiamo al tempio Kotodama\N ad offrire questi 15 capitoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.31,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:33.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,A proposito, Wakaba, \Nqual'è il tuo desiderio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,È un segreto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Però, Onii-chan, ne\N resterai sorpreso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ecco un indizio, Ron-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Finalmente, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.03,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chi è?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.89,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Aiutami, Yutaka-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Akari? Akari, perché sei qui?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:17:00.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Akari-san è tua amica, Onii-chan? Mitsuhashi Akari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Akari! Stai bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quella è la mia schiava.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Non impicciatevi di cose che non vi riguardano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.25,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Chi è lei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Voi due avete \Nvisto il mio segreto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Temo che dovrò\N uccidervi entrambi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Wakaba, stai bene?\N Resisti, Wakaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:42.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Non credo che riuscirò a farcela...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:50.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ti sei occupato di me come se fossi una vera sorella. Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:54.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Che stai dicendo? Io non ti\N abbandono. Perciò resisti!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:18:01.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sai? Io, è da tanto tempo, Onii-chan, che volevo dirti una cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:05.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Che cosa, Wakaba? \NCos'è che volevi dirmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:09.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ti amo, Onii-chan. \NDa tanto tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:15.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ma è come donna, \NOnii-chan, che ti amo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:16.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:23.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Se anche tu mi vedi come\N una donna, baciami Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,È il mio ultimo desiderio...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:32.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Crepate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:37.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Tutti quelli che conoscono il\N mio segreto devono morire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.51,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Fuggi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Salvati, Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.36,Internal,,0,0,0,,Certo! Ora ricordo tutto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:07.25,Internal,,0,0,0,,Io sono la reincarnazione di Yutaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.14,Internal,,0,0,0,,Quei ricordi, i sogni...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:14.21,Internal,,0,0,0,,Ecco perchè tutto dell'isola Oka mi è familiare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:17.99,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:21.95,Internal,,0,0,0,,Volevo vederti, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.17,Internal,,0,0,0,,Io, ti ho sempre aspettato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:29.26,Internal,,0,0,0,,Volevo... volevo rivedere\N il mio Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.27,Internal,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:31.92,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.24,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:39.58,Internal,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:06.33,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, quello è il mio... {posto segreto?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.90,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.51,Internal,,0,0,0,,Wakaba, diventiamo una cosa sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.85,Internal,,0,0,0,,Fallo, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:34.67,Internal,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:38.33,Internal,,0,0,0,,È questa, la sensazione di sentire Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.76,Internal,,0,0,0,,Sono felice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.56,Internal,,0,0,0,,Sono felice anche io, Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.48,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:08.70,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chani! Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.65,Internal,,0,0,0,,Io.... sto venendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.23,Internal,,0,0,0,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.40,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, grazie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:40.42,Internal,,0,0,0,,Non ho nessun rimpianto ora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.30,Internal,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, ti amo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba... finalmente ci siamo riuniti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.35,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,ma di nuovo non ho potuto salvarti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:11.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,L'ultimo capitolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.28,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ora, cosa significa questo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il tempio Kotodama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:27.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Se... Se il mio desiderio\N potesse davvero realizzarsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:29.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il mio desiderio sarebbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il mio desiderio sarebbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.39,0:26:09.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Questa è... l'isola Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.23,0:26:12.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il desiderio di Wakaba-chan deve essersi realizzato.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.73,0:26:13.49,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Già...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:37.20,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.83,0:26:40.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, volevo rivederti!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.93,0:26:43.40,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba? Come..?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.35,0:26:45.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Possibile..?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.23,0:26:53.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Il tempio Kotodama ha realizzato anche il desiderio di Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.36,0:26:55.23,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.34,0:26:56.13,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wakaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.31,0:26:57.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
